= Mail Types =

The following mail types are configured in the mail archive:

{{velocity wiki="true"}}
{{html wiki="true"}}
#set($xwql = "select type.displayName, type.icon from Document doc, doc.object(MailArchiveCode.TypesSettingsClass) as type where doc.space='MailArchivePrefs'")
#set($types = $services.query.xwql($xwql).execute())
|=Name|=Icon
#foreach($type in $types)
|$type[0]|[[image:icon:$type[1]]]
#end
{{/html}}
{{/velocity}}
